orated the 50th anniversary of the [[ANZUS Treaty]] |- |June 11–13, 2002 |June 11–13, 2002 |Addressed a [[Joint Session of Congress]] |- |February 8–10, 2003 |February 8–10, 2003 |Working Visit |- |May 1–3, 2003 |May 1–3, 2003 |Official select visit at [[Crawford Ranch|Crawford]], [[Texas]] |- |June 2–4, 2004 |June 2–4, 2004 |rowspan="2"|Working Visit |- |July 17–19, 2005 |July 17–19, 2005 |- |May 12–17, 2006 |May 12–17, 2006 |Official visit |- |March 27 – April 1, 2008 |March 27 – April 1, 2008 |rowspan="5"| [[Kevin Rudd]] |Working Visit. |- |November 14–15, 2008 |November 14–15, 2008 |Attended the [[2008 G-20 Washington summit|G-20 Economic Summit Meeting]]. |- |March 24, 2009 |March 24, 2009 |Working Visit. |- |September 24–25, 2009 |September 24–25, 2009 |Attended the [[2009 G-20 Pittsburgh summit|G-20 Economic Summit]] in [[Pittsburgh]]. |- |November 30, 2009 |November 30, 2009 |Working Visit. |- |March 7, 2011 |March 7, 2011 |rowspan="3"| [[Julia Gillard]] |Working Visit. Addressed a [[Joint Meeting of Congress]]. |- |November 10–13, 2011 |November 10–13, 2011 |Attended the [[APEC United States 2011|Asia-Pacific Economic and Cooperation Summit]] at [[Honolulu]] and [[Kapolei]], [[Hawaii]]. |- |May 20–21, 2012 |May 20–21, 2012 |Attended the [[2012 Chicago summit|NATO Summit Meeting]] in [[Chicago]] |- |June 12, 2014 |June 12, 2014 |[[Tony Abbott]] |Working Visit. |- |January 19, 2016 |January 19, 2016 |rowspan=4|[[Malcolm Turnbull]] |Working Lunch. |- |September 19, 2016 |September 19, 2016 |Met with [[President Obama]] at the [[UN General Assembly]] meeting in [[New York City]]. |- |May 4, 2017 |May 4, 2017 |Met with [[President Trump]] at the [[Intrepid Sea, Air & Space Museum|U.S.S. Intrepid Museum]] in [[New York City]]. |- |February 23, 2018 |February 23, 2018 |Working Visit. |} </gallery>
